#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Profiles</title>"
msgstr "<title>Profili</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: profiles.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Profiles</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Profili</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With profiles you can save and restore your favorite settings. Several "
"features support profiles, you can have &eg; different panel profiles (work, "
"home, remote connections, &etc;), search profiles, synchroniser profiles, "
"&etc;"
msgstr ""
"S profili lahko shranite in obnovite svoje priljubljene nastavitve. Več "
"funkcij podpira profile, lahko imate &eg; različni profili plošč (služba, "
"dom, oddaljene povezave &etc;), iskalni profili, profili sinhronizatorja, "
"&etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel Profiles"
msgstr "Profili plošč"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A panel profile contains the following: all the tab paths (left or right), "
"the current tab (left or right) and the active panel (left or right). All "
"this information is stored in the <link linkend=\"config_files\">krusaderrc</"
"link> file. You can have several panel profiles, &eg; file management, &FTP; "
"management, home, work, &etc; The panel profile can be <link linkend="
"\"c_panel_profiles\">saved and restored</link> in the <guimenu>Window</"
"guimenu> menu. The <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">default startup profile</"
"link> will be used when starting &krusader;, but you can override it with a "
"command-line option."
msgstr ""
"Profil plošče vsebuje naslednje: vse poti zavihkov (levo ali desno), "
"trenutni zavihek (levo ali desno) in aktivno ploščo (levo ali desno). Vse te "
"informacije so shranjene v datoteki <link linkend=\"config_files"
"\">krusaderrc</link>. Imate lahko več profilov plošče, &eg; upravljanje "
"datotek, &FTP; upravljanje, dom, služba &etc; Profil plošče lahko <link "
"linkend=\"c_panel_profiles\">shranite in obnovite</link> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Okno</guimenu>. <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Privzeti zagonski "
"profil</link> bo uporabljen pri zagonu &krusader;, vendar ga lahko "
"preglasite z možnostjo ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to make changes to a panel profile: you can load that profile, "
"change some settings, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Profiles </guimenuitem></menuchoice> and overwrite that profile."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti profil plošče: lahko naložite ta profil, spremenite "
"nekatere nastavitve, pojdite v <menuchoice><guimenu>Okno</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Profili </guimenuitem></menuchoice> in prepišite ta profil."

#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Profiles"
msgstr "Barvni profili"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Colormaps can be saved and restored with <link linkend=\"konfig-color"
"\">Color Profiles</link>."
msgstr ""
"Barvne zemljevide je mogoče shraniti in obnoviti z <link linkend=\"konfig-"
"color\">barvnimi profili</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-binding Profiles"
msgstr "Profili za vezavo tipk"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keymaps can be saved and restored with <link linkend=\"configure-shortcuts"
"\">Key-binding Profiles</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zemljevide tipk je mogoče shraniti in obnoviti s <link linkend=\"configure-"
"shortcuts\">Profili za vezavo tipk</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Profiles"
msgstr "Iskanje profilov"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you regularly perform the same search operation, you can save the search "
"settings (&eg; include files, exclude files, &etc;) in a <link linkend="
"\"krusearcher\">Search Profile</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če redno izvajate isto iskalno operacijo, lahko nastavitve iskanja (&eg; "
"vključi datoteke, izključi datoteke &etc;) shranite v <link linkend="
"\"krusearcher\">Iskalni profil</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: profiles.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronizer Profiles"
msgstr "Profili sinhronizatorja"

#. Tag: para
#: profiles.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you regularly perform the same synchronize operation, you can save the "
"synchronize settings in a <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer "
"Profile</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če redno izvajate isto operacijo sinhronizacije, lahko nastavitve "
"sinhronizacije shranite v <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Profil "
"sinhronizatorja</link>."
